    translated: "When using Yin attribute techniques, the character enters a Yin attribute state. At this time, the character gains combat bonuses from the Yin attribute and some special effects: 1: Switch to the Yin attribute technique state for this character. While in this state, attacks on characters with a Soft attribute receive an increased damage multiplier. Conversely, attacking those with a Yang inclination results in damage reduction based on the counter coefficient. 2: Characters in a Yin state require compatible Neigong to coordinate with: In harmony or in accordance: The Yin state requires a neigong with a Yin bias to activate and transition into the neigong ‑ Synergistic Technique State. Counteract Effect: If skills in the Yin state use Neigong that leans towards Yang or Softness, the individual will experience disruptions or unobstructed flow of Lifeforce based on the disparity between their Yin and Soft attributes versus their Yang attributes. This is a case of mutual generation: There are no interactions or combinations between internal arts and techniques that produce any special effects. 3"

Conversely, if attacking a character with an affinity for Poison, the damage will be reduced according to the neutralization coefficient. 2: Characters in a Yang state need to pair with compatible properties of Heart Methods, either through mutual enhancement or compatibility: In harmony: The Yang state requires Yang‑dominant Neigong to activate and enter the state of Neigong ‑ Compatible Techniques Status; Opposing Interaction: Using a Yin‑biased or Poison‑biased Neigong skill while in a Yang state can cause the body to experience either Qi and blood congestion or Qi and blood circulation, depending on the discrepancy between the Yang attribute and the Yin or Poison attributes. Conversely, when targeting characters with a tendency towards the Hard attribute, the damage will be reduced by a corresponding counteracting coefficient. 2: Characters in a poisoned state require complementary Neigong for coordination: Concordant or Harmonious: The poison state requires poisonous neigong to be activated and then enter the neigong stage ‑ Synergy state. Neutralizing effect: When skills in a poison state utilize Neigong with an affinity for hardness or Yang, the individual will experience Qi and blood flow being blocked or unimpeded based on the disparity between their poison attribute and the hardness or Yang attributes. This reflects the mutually promoting relationship: There are no life‑generating or destructive internal power and technique combinations without any special effects. 3"

    text: "如何激活经脉：1、满足修为和前置经脉点位条件即可进行激活操作。2、激活有一定概率可获得附加属性。3、激活后可针对附加属性进行洗练，以获得更适合自己的属性。辅助道具：1、在激活或洗练的时候，可以添加辅助素材，包含道具、丹药、密卷和心法。2、辅助素材均可在激活经脉的时候提升成功率。3、其中道具和丹药没有多余的效果，密卷可覆盖激活或洗练时的附加属性，心法可在激活或洗练时添加特殊属性。"
    translated: "How to activate the meridians?: 1, once the cultivation level and prerequisite meridian points are met, activation can be performed. 2, there is a chance to gain additional attributes upon activation. 3, after activation, you can refine these additional attributes to better suit your preferences. Auxiliary item: 1, when activating or refining, additional materials can be added, including items, elixirs, secret scrolls, and Heart Methods. 2, all auxiliary materials can increase the success rate during activation of the meridian channels. 3, among these, items and elixirs have no extra effects; secret scrolls can cover additional attributes activated or refined at that time, while Heart Methods can add special attributes during activation or refinement."

    translated: "Help Information: 1, fulfilling the requirements of cultivation level and prerequisite meridian points allows for activation. 2, upon activation, Heart Method additional special attributes can be added, as well as secret scroll hidden attributes. 3, when adding a secret scroll, it will introduce new conditions required to use the secret scroll; only by additionally meeting these conditions can you activate it. 4, after activation, special and additional attributes can be refined to obtain properties more suited to oneself. Refinement must include corresponding Heart Methods or secret scrolls. 5, once all six meridians on the main interface are activated, operations for Ren and Du Meridians can commence. Only when all eight meridians are activated can one proceed with activating the Five Viscera. 6, by clicking the double fish icon at the center, you can access the configuration interfaces for Ren and Du Meridians as well as Heart Method settings. The outer circle represents the points of Ren and Du Meridians, while the center is for Heart Method configurations. 7, configuring a Heart Method will grant the corresponding true attributes."

All eight meridians must be activated before proceeding with the Five Viscera activation. 6, clicking on the double fish icon at the center enters the Ren and Du Meridians configuration interface, with the outer circle representing Ren and Du points, and the center for Heart Method configuration. 7, configuring a Heart Method will yield the corresponding true attributes."

- raw: "117501#WineGameView/Tips/des#				    提示1.每次叫点，需要在对方叫的点数或者个数上至少加1。2.拥有顺子时则视为零个骰子。3.拥有五个完全相同的点数的骰子时，在该点数的个数上加2。4.点数1可以被当作任意骰子使用。5.可通过叫一重新开始，此时点数1只能被当做1使用，且每次叫点，需要在对方叫的点数或者个数上至少加2。6.可通过“开”来结束对饮，若对方叫的点数的个数小于双方该点数的个数相加时则被开的一方获胜，反之若大于双方该点数的个数相加时则开的一方获胜。#"
  splits:
  - split: 2
    text: "				    提示1.每次叫点，需要在对方叫的点数或者个数上至少加1。2.拥有顺子时则视为零个骰子。3.拥有五个完全相同的点数的骰子时，在该点数的个数上加2。4.点数1可以被当作任意骰子使用。5.可通过叫一重新开始，此时点数1只能被当做1使用，且每次叫点，需要在对方叫的点数或者个数上至少加2。6.可通过“开”来结束对饮，若对方叫的点数的个数小于双方该点数的个数相加时则被开的一方获胜，反之若大于双方该点数的个数相加时则开的一方获胜。"
    translated: "Each time a number is called using Prompt 1., it must be at least 1 higher than the number or count called by the opponent. If 2. has a sequence, it counts as zero dice. If 3. rolls five dice of the same number, they add 2 to that number's count. The number 4. 1 can be used as any die. Using Prompt 5., you may restart the call, at which point the number 1 can only be used as 1, and each time a number is called, it must be at least 2 higher than the opponent's called number or count. By saying open, 6. can end the game; if the opponent's called number count is less than the sum of both players' counts for that number, the opener wins; otherwise, if it exceeds the total count from both sides, the player who was opened upon wins."
